evidence.efficacyEvidence: In a preclinical study, RO4987655 reduced Erk phosphorylation and inhibited growth of gastric cancer cell lines harboring an FGFR2 amplification and a KDM7A-BRAF fusion in culture (PMID: 30045926).

references.title: Acquired JHDM1D-BRAF Fusion Confers Resistance to FGFR Inhibition in FGFR2-Amplified Gastric Cancer.
